      "category": "team",
      "content": "Shopify merchants can purchase and manage domains through Shopify. As part of this service, shop owners can delegate the `Transfer domain to another Shopify store` permission to shop staff, which allows staff to transfer domains from one shop to another. \n\nStaff members without the `Transfer domain to another Shopify store` permission were able to transfer the shops domain to another provider.  ",
